    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>εἴτε</corr><sic>ητε</sic></choice> τὴν κονίαν, <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> μεθ᾽ <choice><corr>ὑγιεί-

    <lb n="12"/>ας</corr><sic>υγιας</sic></choice> ἐὰν <sic>αν</sic> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐ</supplied>γὼ ἔλθω πρὸς ὑμᾶς, <sic> <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> </sic> 

    <lb n="13"/>εὕρω πάντα <choice><corr>ἕτοιμα</corr><sic>ετυμα</sic></choice>.  <choice><corr>οἴδατε</corr><sic>υδατε</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="14"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 8.31">τὴν ἀνάγκην</lem><rdg><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ειν ἀναγ<gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>ν</rdg></app> τῆς στρατείας· 

    <lb n="15"/><choice><corr>καὶ ἂν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> εἰς τοῦτο <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὑ</supplied>πηρετήσατέ μοι 

    <lb n="16"/>ὅπως ε<gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/>υ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λ</unclear>ης μετ᾽ αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="17"/>ἕως ὅτου ἡ <choice><corr>ἑτοιμασία</corr><sic>ετυμασι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied></sic></choice> γένηται μετὰ τὴν κατασπορὰν καὶ <choice><corr>εὐσ-

